I think we should define a PlayerComponent interface, which contains static methods for building a player TextComponent.
So something like this:
interface PlayerComponent {
  static TextComponent of(Player player);
  static TextComponent of(UUID playerId); // could show "Unknown"
  static TextComponent of(CommandSender sender);  // could show "Console" when null or console sender
}

